<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Crystal Car Care - Premium Automotive Services</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #003087;
            --secondary: #00205b;
            --accent: #00a8e8;
            --light: #f8f9fa;
            --dark: #1a252f;
            --success: #2ecc71;
            --neutral: #121212; /* updated to match navbar background */
            --spacing-xs: 0.5rem;
            --spacing-sm: 1rem;
            --spacing-md: 1.5rem;
            --spacing-lg: 2rem;
            --spacing-xl: 3rem;
            --border-radius: 12px;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
            --shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }


        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: var(--neutral);
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        /* Section Titles */
        .section-title h2 {
            color: #FFD700; /* gold for titles */
        }

        /* Section Description / Paragraph */
        .section-title p {
            color: #e0e0e0; /* light gray for text */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            min-height: 85vh; /* full viewport height */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.55), rgba(0,0,0,0.55)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
            color: #FFD700; /* gold theme */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-content {
            width: 100%; /* full width of hero */
            max-width: 1200px; /* optional to limit max width */
            margin: 0 auto; /* center it horizontally */
            padding: 0 2rem; /* optional padding so text doesn't touch edges */
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            color: #e0e0e0; /* light gray for readability */
        }


        /* Services */
        .services {
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
        }

        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

            .service-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-8px);
                box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            }

        .service-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover .service-img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .service-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            color: #FFD700; /* gold for service titles */
        }

        .service-card a.btn-outline {
            border-color: #FFD700; /* gold border */
            color: #FFD700; /* gold text */
            background-color: transparent;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

            .service-card a.btn-outline:hover {
                background-color: #FFD700; /* gold background on hover */
                color: #111; /* dark text on hover */
                border-color: #FFD700; /* maintain gold border */
            }

        .service-card p {
            color: #e0e0e0; /* light gray for descriptions */
        }

        /* Features */
        .features {
            background: #111; /* dark background like hero */
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background: #1a1a1a; /* dark card background */
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            color: #FFD700; /* gold text for headings inside cards */
        }

            .feature-item p {
                color: #e0e0e0; /* light gray for description text */
            }

            .feature-item:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #FFD700; /* gold icons */
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-item:hover .feature-icon {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(10deg);
        }

        .cta {
            background: #111; /* dark background like navbar */
            color: #FFD700; /* gold text */
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .cta h2 {
                color: #FFD700; /* gold title */
            }

            .cta p {
                color: #e0e0e0; /* light gray description */
            }

            .cta .btn-light {
                background: #FFD700; /* gold button */
                color: #111; /* dark text on button */
                padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
                border-radius: var(--border-radius);
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: 0.3s;
                border: none;
            }

                .cta .btn-light:hover {
                    background: #FFA500; /* darker gold on hover */
                    color: #111;
                    transform: scale(1.05);
                }

        /* Responsive */
        @@media(max-width:768px) {
            .services-grid, .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Premium Automotive Care</h1>
            <p>Your car deserves the best. Experience luxury car detailing and services like never before.</p>
            <a href="/User/Booking" class="btn-cta">Book Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Our Services</h2>
                <p>Comprehensive automotive services to keep your vehicle in pristine condition.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520340356584-f9917d1eea6f?q=80&w=1331&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Car Wash" class="service-img">
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Car Wash</h3>
                        <p>Professional exterior and interior cleaning that leaves your vehicle sparkling clean.</p>
                        <a href="/services/carwash" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618783129985-dd97dbe4ad99?q=80&w=687&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Mechanic Services" class="service-img">
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Mechanic Services</h3>
                        <p>Expert maintenance and repairs by certified technicians using premium parts.</p>
                        <a href="/services/mechanic" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1471289549423-04adaecfa1f1?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Detailing Services" class="service-img">
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Detailing Services</h3>
                        <p>Premium detailing and paint protection to enhance your vehicle's appearance.</p>
                        <a href="/services/additional" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features" id="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
                <p>Discover what sets Crystal Car Care apart as the premier choice for automotive enthusiasts.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-clock feature-icon"></i><h3>Quick Service</h3><p>Efficient, high-quality service that respects your time.</p></div>
                <div class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-star feature-icon"></i><h3>Quality Guarantee</h3><p>Every service comes with our commitment to satisfaction.</p></div>
                <div class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-tools feature-icon"></i><h3>Expert Technicians</h3><p>Certified professionals with extensive industry experience.</p></div>
                <div class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign feature-icon"></i><h3>Competitive Pricing</h3><p>Premium services at prices that offer exceptional value.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta" id="cta">
        <h2>Elevate Your Vehicle's Care Today</h2>
        <p>Schedule your appointment with Crystal Car Care and experience unparalleled automotive services.</p>
        <a href="/booking" class="btn-light">Schedule Appointment</a>
    </section>

</body>
</html>

